Variables
============
$blue: #0000ff;


Rules
======
Embedding
$baseClass: "something"

#{$baseClass}somethingelse // string concatenation

Structure
nav {
    font-size: etc
    ul {
        list-style etc
        li {
            float etc
        }
    }
}

Parent selector (&) to mix with Parent
a {
    text-decoration etc
    $:hover {
        text-decoration etc
    }
}

Nest properties 
.button {
    font: {
        family etc
        size etc
    }
}

